  "description": {
    "zh-TW": "專業的兒童抗生素劑量計算工具，支援多種抗生素和抗病毒藥物的劑量計算，幫助醫療人員快速準確計算用藥劑量",
    "en": "Professional pediatric antibiotic dose calculation tool supporting multiple antibiotics and antiviral medications, helping healthcare professionals calculate accurate dosages quickly",
    "ja": "複数の抗生物質と抗ウイルス薬の用量計算をサポートする専門的な小児抗生物質用量計算ツール、医療従事者が迅速かつ正確に投薬量を計算するのを支援"
  },
  "category": "pediatrics",
  "metadata": {
    "difficulty": "intermediate",
    "tags": ["pediatrics", "antibiotics", "antivirals", "dose-calculation", "infection", "cefixime", "baktar", "levofloxacin", "cephalexin", "azithromycin", "minocycline", "doxycycline", "acyclovir"],
    "author": "Astro Clinical Platform",
    "license": "MIT",
    "keywords": ["pediatric", "antibiotic", "antiviral", "dose", "calculation", "infection"]
  },
  "medical": {
    "specialty": ["Pediatrics", "Family Medicine", "Internal Medicine", "Infectious Disease"],
    "evidenceLevel": "A",
    "clinicalGuidelines": {
      "zh-TW": "基於兒科抗生素使用指引和感染症治療準則，提供常用抗生素和抗病毒藥物的標準劑量計算。包含抗細菌藥物（Cefixime、Baktar、Levofloxacin、Cephalexin、Azithromycin、Minocycline、Doxycycline）和抗病毒藥物（Acyclovir）的劑量建議。",
      "en": "Based on pediatric antibiotic guidelines and infectious disease treatment standards, providing standard dose calculations for commonly used antibiotics and antiviral medications. Includes dosing recommendations for antibacterial drugs (Cefixime, Baktar, Levofloxacin, Cephalexin, Azithromycin, Minocycline, Doxycycline) and antiviral drugs (Acyclovir).",
      "ja": "小児抗生物質ガイドラインと感染症治療基準に基づき、一般的に使用される抗生物質と抗ウイルス薬の標準用量計算を提供。抗菌薬（セフィキシム、バクター、レボフロキサシン、セファレキシン、アジスロマイシン、ミノサイクリン、ドキシサイクリン）と抗ウイルス薬（アシクロビル）の用量推奨を含む。"
    },
    "references": [
      {
        "title": "Pediatric Antimicrobial Stewardship Guidelines",
        "authors": ["American Academy of Pediatrics"],
        "journal": "Pediatrics",
        "year": "2023",
        "doi": "10.1542/peds.2023-061891"
      },
      {
        "title": "Nelson's Pediatric Antimicrobial Therapy",
        "authors": ["John S. Bradley", "John D. Nelson"],
        "publisher": "American Academy of Pediatrics",
        "year": "2023",
        "edition": "29th"
      }
    ]
  },
  "ui": {
    "fields": [
      {
        "id": "weight",
        "type": "number",
        "label": {
          "zh-TW": "兒童體重",
          "en": "Child Weight",
          "ja": "小児体重"
        },
        "helpText": {
          "zh-TW": "請輸入兒童的體重（公斤）",
          "en": "Enter the child's weight in kilograms",
          "ja": "小児の体重をキログラムで入力してください"
        },
        "required": true,
        "validation": {
          "min": 1,
          "max": 100
        },
        "unit": {
          "zh-TW": "公斤",
          "en": "kg",
          "ja": "kg"
        },
        "placeholder": {
          "zh-TW": "例如：15",
          "en": "e.g., 15",
          "ja": "例：15"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "age",
        "type": "number",
        "label": {
          "zh-TW": "兒童年齡",
          "en": "Child Age",
          "ja": "小児年齢"
        },
        "helpText": {
          "zh-TW": "請輸入兒童的年齡（歲），部分藥物計算所需",
          "en": "Enter the child's age in years, required for some medications",
          "ja": "小児の年齢を歳で入力してください。一部の薬物計算に必要です"
        },
        "required": false,
        "validation": {
          "min": 0,
          "max": 18
        },
        "unit": {
          "zh-TW": "歲",
          "en": "years",
          "ja": "歳"
        },
        "placeholder": {
          "zh-TW": "部分藥物計算所需",
          "en": "Required for some medications",
          "ja": "一部の薬物に必要"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "form",
        "type": "radio",
        "label": {
          "zh-TW": "藥物劑型",
          "en": "Drug Form",
          "ja": "薬物剤形"
        },
        "helpText": {
          "zh-TW": "選擇藥物的劑型",
          "en": "Select the drug form",
          "ja": "薬物の剤形を選択"
        },
        "required": true,
        "defaultValue": "powder",
        "options": [
          {
            "value": "powder",
            "label": {
              "zh-TW": "藥粉",
              "en": "Powder",
              "ja": "粉薬"
            }
          },
          {
            "value": "pill",
            "label": {
              "zh-TW": "藥錠/膠囊",
              "en": "Tablet/Capsule",
              "ja": "錠剤/カプセル"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "days",
        "type": "select",
        "label": {
          "zh-TW": "治療天數",
          "en": "Treatment Days",
          "ja": "治療日数"
        },
        "helpText": {
          "zh-TW": "選擇總治療天數",
          "en": "Select total treatment days",
          "ja": "総治療日数を選択"
        },
        "required": true,
        "defaultValue": "3",
        "options": [
          {
            "value": "1",
            "label": {
              "zh-TW": "1 天",
              "en": "1 Day",
              "ja": "1日"
            }
          },
          {
            "value": "2",
            "label": {
              "zh-TW": "2 天",
              "en": "2 Days",
              "ja": "2日"
            }
          },
          {
            "value": "3",
            "label": {
              "zh-TW": "3 天",
              "en": "3 Days",
              "ja": "3日"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "frequency",
        "type": "select",
        "label": {
          "zh-TW": "用藥頻次",
          "en": "Dosing Frequency",
          "ja": "投与頻度"
        },
        "helpText": {
          "zh-TW": "選擇每日用藥次數",
          "en": "Select daily dosing frequency",
          "ja": "1日の投与回数を選択"
